                        X.F71804 AS "Functia", F.F00305 AS "Subcompanie",G.F00406 AS "Filiala",H.F00507 AS "Sectie",I.F00608 AS "Departament" , "Rol", "RolDenumire"
                        FROM (
                        SELECT A.F10003, 0 AS "Rol",  COALESCE((SELECT COALESCE("Alias", "Denumire") FROM "tblSupervizori" WHERE "Id"=0),'Angajat') AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                        UNION
                        SELECT A.F10003, B."IdSuper" AS "Rol", CASE WHEN D."Alias" IS NOT NULL AND D."Alias" <> '' THEN D."Alias" ELSE D."Denumire" END AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" B ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" D ON D."Id" = B."IdSuper"
                        WHERE B."IdUser"= ) B

                                FROM "MeniuLinii" B

                        SELECT A.F10003, 0 AS "Rol",  COALESCE((SELECT COALESCE("Alias", "Denumire") FROM "tblSupervizori" WHERE "Id"=0),'Angajat') AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                        UNION
                        SELECT A.F10003, B."IdSuper" AS "Rol", CASE WHEN D."Alias" IS NOT NULL AND D."Alias" <> '' THEN D."Alias" ELSE D."Denumire" END AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" B ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" D ON D."Id" = B."IdSuper"
                        WHERE B."IdUser"= 3) B                        
                        INNER JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        LEFT JOIN F718 X ON A.F10071=X.F71802
                        LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                        LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                        LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                        LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607

                        SELECT A.F10003, 0 AS "Rol",  COALESCE((SELECT COALESCE("Alias", "Denumire") FROM "tblSupervizori" WHERE "Id"=0),'Angajat') AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                        UNION
                        SELECT A.F10003, B."IdSuper" AS "Rol", CASE WHEN D."Alias" IS NOT NULL AND D."Alias" <> '' THEN D."Alias" ELSE D."Denumire" END AS "RolDenumire"
                        FROM F100 A
                        INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" B ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" D ON D."Id" = B."IdSuper"
                        WHERE B."IdUser"= 3) B                        
                        INNER JOIN F100 A ON A.F10003=B.F10003
                        LEFT JOIN F718 X ON A.F10071=X.F71802
                        LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                        LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405
                        LEFT JOIN F005 H ON A.F10006 = H.F00506
                        LEFT JOIN F006 I ON A.F10007 = I.F00607

Data:    17.02.2022 15:18:38
Pagina:    General
Eveni:     IncarcaDT
Eroarea:   SELECT B."IdMeniu", B."Parinte", B."Nume", B."Imagine", B."Ordine", E."Pagina", B."Descriere", B."StareMobil", B."NumeMobil", B."OrdineMobil"
                                FROM "MeniuLinii" B
                                INNER JOIN "relGrupMeniu2" C ON B."IdMeniu" = C."IdMeniu"
                                INNER JOIN "relGrupUser" D ON C."IdGrup" = D."IdGrup"
                                LEFT JOIN "tblMeniuri" E ON E."Id" = B."IdNomen"
                                WHERE D."IdUser" = @1 AND B."Stare" = 1
                                GROUP BY B."Parinte", B."IdMeniu", B."Nume", B."Imagine", B."Ordine", E."Pagina", B."Descriere", B."StareMobil", B."NumeMobil", B."OrdineMobil"
                                ORDER BY B."Parinte", B."Ordine"

                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,

                                INNER JOIN "F100Supervizori" J ON B.F10003 = J.F10003 AND C."IdSuper" = (-1 * J."IdSuper") AND J."DataInceput" <= GETDATE() AND GETDATE() <= J."DataSfarsit"                               
                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802                                
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202                                
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304

                                LEFT JOIN F008 L ON X.F100959 = L.F00809                                  
                                WHERE J."IdUser" = 3

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra29" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra29" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra29")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=29) + '=' + "CampExtra29" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra30" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra30" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra30")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=30) + '=' + "CampExtra30" + '; ' ELSE '' END + 
                                
                    CASE WHEN "OraInceput" IS NOT NULL AND "OraSfarsit" IS NOT NULL THEN 
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa", 
                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,
                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 3 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 3
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99   and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser=3 and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                (
                                SELECT Y.F70102 FROM "Ptj_Cereri" X
                                INNER JOIN USERS Y ON X.F10003=Y.F10003
                                WHERE X."IdStare"=3 AND X."Inlocuitor" = -99
                                AND CONVERT(date,X."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,X."DataSfarsit")
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=3 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"

                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 2 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 2
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99   and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser=2 and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=2 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"

                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 7 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 7
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 7
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> 7   and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser=7 and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=7 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +

                                AS "DateConcatenate", COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa", 
                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,

                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                WHERE A.F10003 = 7

                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",

                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1

                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"

                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                                LEFT JOIN F718 D ON A.F10071 = D.F71802
                                LEFT JOIN F002 E ON A.F10002 = E.F00202
                                LEFT JOIN F003 F ON A.F10004 = F.F00304
                                LEFT JOIN F004 G ON A.F10005 = G.F00405

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra30" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra30" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra30")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=30) + '=' + "CampExtra30" + '; ' ELSE '' END + 
                                
                    CASE WHEN "OraInceput" IS NOT NULL AND "OraSfarsit" IS NOT NULL THEN 
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa", 
                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,
                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 3 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = -99
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 3
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> -99   and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser=3 and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=3 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."Actiune" = 1 AND A."IdStare" IN (1,2) ) X

                                AS "DateConcatenate", COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa", 
                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,
                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" =  AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <>    and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser= and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"= AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"
                            UNION 
                            SELECT -1 AS "Rol", 'Toate' AS "RolDenumire", 0 AS "Ordin"   ) Y WHERE Y."Rol" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY "Ordin"

                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,

                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"= AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"
                            UNION 
                            SELECT -1 AS "Rol", 'Toate' AS "RolDenumire", 0 AS "Ordin"   ) Y WHERE Y."Rol" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY "Ordin"

                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END

                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,
                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" =  AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" =

                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"= AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"
                            UNION 
                            SELECT -1 AS "Rol", 'Toate' AS "RolDenumire", 0 AS "Ordin"   ) Y WHERE Y."Rol" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY "Ordin"

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra29" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra29" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra29")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=29) + '=' + "CampExtra29" + '; ' ELSE '' END +
                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra30" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra30" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra30")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=30) + '=' + "CampExtra30" + '; ' ELSE '' END + 
                                
                    CASE WHEN "OraInceput" IS NOT NULL AND "OraSfarsit" IS NOT NULL THEN 
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa", 
                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,
                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" =  AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <>    and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser= and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"= AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"
                            UNION 
                            SELECT -1 AS "Rol", 'Toate' AS "RolDenumire", 0 AS "Ordin"   ) Y WHERE Y."Rol" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY "Ordin"

                                UNION

                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"= AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"
                            UNION 
                            SELECT -1 AS "Rol", 'Toate' AS "RolDenumire", 0 AS "Ordin"   ) Y WHERE Y."Rol" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY "Ordin"

                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                -99

                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"= AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"
                            UNION 
                            SELECT -1 AS "Rol", 'Toate' AS "RolDenumire", 0 AS "Ordin"   ) Y WHERE Y."Rol" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY "Ordin"

                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile

                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <>    and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser= and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"= AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"
                            UNION 
                            SELECT -1 AS "Rol", 'Toate' AS "RolDenumire", 0 AS "Ordin"   ) Y WHERE Y."Rol" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY "Ordin"

                                AS "DateConcatenate", COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa", 
                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,
                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile

                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"

                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +

                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa", 
                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,
                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" =  AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",

                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <>    and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser= and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"= AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"
                            UNION 
                            SELECT -1 AS "Rol", 'Toate' AS "RolDenumire", 0 AS "Ordin"   ) Y WHERE Y."Rol" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY "Ordin"

                    CASE WHEN "OraInceput" IS NOT NULL AND "OraSfarsit" IS NOT NULL THEN 
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END

                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,
                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile

                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" =  AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <>    and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser= and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"= AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"
                            UNION 
                            SELECT -1 AS "Rol", 'Toate' AS "RolDenumire", 0 AS "Ordin"   ) Y WHERE Y."Rol" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY "Ordin"

                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"

                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"

                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" =  AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <>    and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser= and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"= AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"
                            UNION 
                            SELECT -1 AS "Rol", 'Toate' AS "RolDenumire", 0 AS "Ordin"   ) Y WHERE Y."Rol" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY "Ordin"

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra28" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra28" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra28")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=28) + '=' + "CampExtra28" + '; ' ELSE '' END +

                                CASE WHEN "CampExtra30" IS NOT NULL  AND "CampExtra30" IS NOT NULL  AND RTRIM(LTRIM("CampExtra30")) <> ''  THEN (SELECT "Denumire" FROM "Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig" WHERE "IdAbsenta"=A."IdAbsenta" AND "IdCampExtra"=30) + '=' + "CampExtra30" + '; ' ELSE '' END + 
                                
                    CASE WHEN "OraInceput" IS NOT NULL AND "OraSfarsit" IS NOT NULL THEN 
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraInceput")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraInceput")) + ' - ' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(HOUR, "OraSfarsit")) + ':' +
                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa", COALESCE(A."CampExtra19",0) AS "CampExtra19",  "CampExtra20", 
                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,
                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" =  AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1

                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A

                                (
                                -99
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"= AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"
                            UNION 
                            SELECT -1 AS "Rol", 'Toate' AS "RolDenumire", 0 AS "Ordin"   ) Y WHERE Y."Rol" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY "Ordin"

                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 100012 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 100012
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 100012
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <> 100012   and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser=100012 and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                SELECT Y.F70102 FROM "Ptj_Cereri" X
                                INNER JOIN USERS Y ON X.F10003=Y.F10003
                                WHERE X."IdStare"=3 AND X."Inlocuitor" = 100012
                                AND CONVERT(date,X."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,X."DataSfarsit")
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"=100012 AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2100-01-01') AND CONVERT(date,'2022-04-01') <= A."DataSfarsit"  ORDER BY A.TIME DESC

                                AS "DateConcatenate", COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa", A."CampExtra19",  "CampExtra20", 
                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,
                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" =  AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" C ON (-1 * B."IdSuper")= C."Id"     --AND COALESCE(C."ModululCereriAbsente", 0) = 1
                                WHERE A.F10003 <>    and abs(b.IdSuper) = (select max(abs(IdSuper)) from Ptj_CereriIstoric where idUser= and idcerere=a.id  and Pozitie <> 0 AND IdStare <> -1) 
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (
                                SELECT Y.F70102 FROM "Ptj_Cereri" X
                                INNER JOIN USERS Y ON X.F10003=Y.F10003
                                WHERE X."IdStare"=3 AND X."Inlocuitor" = 
                                AND CONVERT(date,X."DataInceput") <= CONVERT(date,GetDate()) AND CONVERT(date,GetDate()) <= CONVERT(date,X."DataSfarsit")
                                )
                                WHERE 1 = 1  
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"= AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" Q ON A."TrimiteLa" = Q."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"
                            UNION 
                            SELECT -1 AS "Rol", 'Toate' AS "RolDenumire", 0 AS "Ordin"   ) Y WHERE Y."Rol" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY "Ordin"

                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS Rol,
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."IdSuper" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" IN 
                                (SELECT "IdUser" FROM "tblDelegari" WHERE COALESCE("IdModul",-99)=1 AND "IdDelegat"= AND "DataInceput" <= GetDate() AND GetDate() <= "DataSfarsit") ) A
                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"

                                LEFT JOIN F100 D ON A."Inlocuitor" = D.F10003
                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1 ) X GROUP BY "Rol", "RolDenumire"
                            UNION 
                            SELECT -1 AS "Rol", 'Toate' AS "RolDenumire", 0 AS "Ordin"   ) Y WHERE Y."Rol" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY "Ordin"

                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",

                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",

                                WHERE 1 = 1

                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"

                                INNER JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003 = B.F10003
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" C ON A."IdAbsenta" = C."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" M ON C."CompensareBanca" = M."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_tblAbsente" N ON C."CompensarePlata" = N."Id"

                                LEFT JOIN "tblSupervizori" E ON A."Rol" = E."Id"
                                LEFT JOIN F003 ON F00304 = B.F10004
                                WHERE 1=1  AND A."DataInceput" <= CONVERT(date,'2100-01-01') AND CONVERT(date,'2022-04-01') <= A."DataSfarsit"  ORDER BY A.TIME DESC

                    SUBSTRING('00', 1, 2 - LEN(CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")))) + CONVERT(nvarchar(2), DATEPART(MINUTE, "OraSfarsit")) + '; ' ELSE '' END
                                AS "DateConcatenate", COALESCE(A."CampBifa",0) AS "CampBifa", CONVERT(INTEGER, A."CampExtra19") AS "CampExtra19",  "CampExtra20", 
                    (SELECT TOP 1 Valoare FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_Valoare,
                    (SELECT TOP 1 NrZile  FROM Ptj_CereriDrepturi DR WHERE DR.IdAbs IN (A.IdAbsenta,-13) AND DR.IdStare IN (A.IdStare, -13) AND DR.IdRol IN (A.Rol, -13) AND DR.IdActiune IN (3, -13) ORDER BY DR.IdAbs DESC, DR.IdRol DESC, DR.IdStare DESC) AS Anulare_NrZile
                                FROM (SELECT A.*, 0 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN (A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) OR B."IdCerere" IS NULL) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                LEFT JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdUser" = 100012 AND B."IdStare" IN (1, 2, 3, 4)
                                WHERE A.F10003 = 100012
                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN C."Id" IS NOT NULL THEN C."Id" ELSE (CASE WHEN B."IdSuper" > 0 THEN 76 ELSE C."Id" END) END AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN (A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
                                FROM "Ptj_Cereri" A
                                INNER JOIN "Ptj_CereriIstoric" B ON A."Id" = B."IdCerere" AND B."Pozitie" <> 0 AND B."IdStare" <> -1 AND B."IdUser" = 100012

                                UNION
                                SELECT A.*, 78 AS "Rol",
                                CASE WHEN A."IdStare" IN (-1, 0, 3) THEN 0 ELSE (CASE WHEN(A."Pozitie" + 1) = B."Pozitie" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) END AS "Actiune"
